{"tid":859612,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆好撚爛賭，屋企比人淋紅油","createTime":"2018-10-12T15:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T09:19:32.000Z","uid":210524,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a59719a0c9b437ea7566ab33febc56c0db4b1c8","tid":859612,"uid":210524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"話說老豆賭乜輸乜<br />\n輸左就問財仔借錢<br />\n本身都係借幾千，一岀糧就連本帶利還清<br />\n但今次佢又賭輸波，仲問財仔借左5萬<br />\n但佢老闆拖糧，幾個月冇糧岀<br />\n結果今日有人上黎收數，話啲利息加埋已經超過<br />\n港幣433333<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母仲同佢地嘈<br />\n話冇可能架，我老公邊有差你地咁多<br />\n結果屋企比人淋紅油<br />\n老母見到仲嚇到尖叫<br />\n老母今日已經無笑過<br />\n即係佢好唔開心<br />\n宜家仲匿埋係一邊到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家認為，需唔需要報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014c02a6dbeb3a506b6f482aef13562520691145","tid":859612,"uid":54270,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"433333都後門上U grad埋 你仲鞭屍唔厭咩"},{"pid":"10fac7f8f0bd0aca81c17ffd0ad4f5bbfb38d96d","tid":859612,"uid":59192,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"樓主依排做乜係咁出膠post提433333"},{"pid":"4a8452743fcdd1641177beb481e7990d997b3cdf","tid":859612,"uid":193110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:05:37.000Z","msg":"報埋拖糧嗰個腦細"},{"pid":"b68d83dd8863257da3ef050508b07d034b4cebec","tid":859612,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4836a686db4dfa60877fe07a368560948ffd47aa","tid":859612,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"014c02a6dbeb3a506b6f482aef13562520691145","tid":859612,"uid":54270,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"433333都後門上U grad埋 你仲鞭屍唔厭咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:08:39.00